Comment: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:42.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}「{\k1}我{\k1}需{\k1}要{\k1}你{\k1}，{\k1}我{\k1}需{\k1}要{\k1}你{\k1}」{\k1}这{\k1}是{\k1}秘{\k1}密
Comment: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:50.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}拜{\k1}托{\k1}请{\k1}不{\k1}要{\k1}停{\k1}下{\k1}来
Comment: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:54.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}你{\k1}与{\k1}我{\k1}共{\k1}同{\k1}奏{\k1}响{\k1}的{\k1}旋{\k1}律
Comment: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:04.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}时{\k1}刻{\k1}都{\k1}要{\k1}在{\k1}我{\k1}身{\k1}边
Comment: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:08.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}S{\k1}t{\k1}r{\k1}a{\k1}w{\k1}b{\k1}e{\k1}r{\k1}r{\k1}y{\k1}·{\k1}发{\k1}射{\k1}·{\k1}s{\k1}t{\k1}r{\k1}a{\k1}w{\k1}b{\k1}e{\k1}r{\k1}r{\k1}y{\k1}·{\k1}l{\k1}i{\k1}e
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,----------ED----------
Comment: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:45.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,その腕に絡んだ時計の針は
Comment: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:46.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Close-set mind
Comment: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:51.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,狂わないなんて信じていないで
Comment: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:58.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,進もうと急かすような秒針
Comment: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:59.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Close-set mind
Comment: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:04.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,巻き戻そう 抓んだ竜頭回し
Comment: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:08.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,奇想夢譚になっていく
Comment: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:11.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,曖昧が依然あるなら
Comment: 0,0:22:11.52,0:22:14.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,触れて確かめてしまえばいいよ
Comment: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:17.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,現実を脱がせて
Comment: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:20.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Let me hightail it out of here
Comment: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,繰り返すほど牴牾しい
Comment: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:30.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,儚いって知りながら 求めてしまう
Comment: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:33.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,背徳の夢
Comment: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:45.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,缠绕在你腕上的时针
Comment: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:51.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,毋庸置疑会行至疯狂
Comment: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:58.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,仿佛在催促前行的秒针
Comment: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:04.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,拧动发条 让我们逆转时光吧
Comment: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:08.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,坠入梦幻奇谭
Comment: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:11.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,若暧昧仍旧存在
Comment: 0,0:22:11.52,0:22:14.49,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,亲自触碰来确认这一切
Comment: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:17.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,褪去现实的桎梏
Comment: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.85,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,越是重演便越显矛盾
Comment: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:30.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,明知虚幻 却仍执于追寻
Comment: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:33.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,这场背德之梦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,----------STAFF----------
